query:
query GetRenditions($limit: Int, $nextToken: String, $country: Country!, $fromDate: String!, $toDate: String!, $filter: RenditionFilterInput) {
  getRenditions(
    limit: $limit
    nextToken: $nextToken
    country: $country
    fromDate: $fromDate
    toDate: $toDate
    filter: $filter
  ) {
    renditions {
      assetType
      country
      ID
      createdAt
      createdBy
      isRenditionMoved
      modifiedAt
      modifiedBy
      renditionFileName
      userName
      wochitRenditionStatus
      errorMessage
      mamAssetInfoReferenceId
      iconikAssetUrl
      seriesName
      renditionAssetId
      __typename
    }
    nextToken
    scannedCount
    __typename
  }
}
